data.description: Spacious home on over an acre of yard. Over-sized two car garage can be also used as a workshop. Cool off on those hot Florida days in the fenced-in in-ground pool area.The 3 bedroom home itself boast a large family room. Spacious eat in kitchen with both breakfast bar and nook is light and bright which opens up to the patio. Granite counter-tops in the kitchen and bathrooms. NO HOA or CDD. Close to I-75, shopping and schools! Move in ready! Schedule a showing today!
